    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks for the discussion here.\r\n\r\n> I'm not excited about the proposal here, which feels like a work-around for fundamentally broken broadcasting behavior rather than a fix of the root cause.\r\n\r\nMy proposal was afaik a minor fix for a common problem, which people like me have _now_. But, I've learned, that even this addition would mean a lot of trouble/confusion to others. So, I agree with @shoyer and @jreback that this issue is reasonable, but also too profound."
